{
  "stem": "16930.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 232.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In fact, it's conceivable that if their father or-- or-- or that their grandfather or grandmother were Jewish, and the parents were not, they may have gone to regular churches, you know, and weren't even aware of being Jewish, some of them, you know-- and may even have resented being put into the situation of being Jewish.",
      "word_count": 57
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At Barham House, they had classes-- classes in English-- like school classes in English and in other subjects.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So of course, having-- having had the experience of going to this other-- my first place, going to regular school and learning English quite well from the other kids, you know, and from school, I had some-- I had-- I had some knowledge of English already.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they put me to one of the higher classes, where I was with some of the older children.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The age range of children from the Kindertransport-- I think anywhere from age three to age 17.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I imagine here at Barham House probably from age seven or eight till age 17.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I made some friends.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah, I had some-- I had some friends.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there were some friends.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And in fact-- and there was a synagogue there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There were a few of the children who went to the synagogue for services, Friday night Sabbaths.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then these-- a couple of these friends, when they distributed all of us, they were going to go to an-- a hostel.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I'll tell you what a hostel is in a minute.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The Orthodox hostel.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they told the-- and I wasn't assigned yet.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So they told the chaplain I got assigned to that Orthodox hostel also, which had a-- a great impact on my life until this day.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "In a hostel-- we-- we call in-- in-- in America a group home.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
